RALPH: Add multi-fee collection with session-based invoicing (Issue #6)

PRD: Issue #6 — Multi-Fee Collection with Session-Based Invoicing

Key decisions:
- New feeCollectionSessions table stores one session per invoice (INV- prefix)
- collectFees mutation atomically creates session + N transactions + updates N fees
- No partial payments: each fee collected in full (balance amount)
- Single payment mode per session, server-stamped transaction date
- Campus auto-filled from student's current enrollment
- Sequential month enforcement for future month removal in dialog
- billingPeriod (YYYY-MM) on studentFees for recurring fee identification
- sessionId on feeTransactions links transactions back to their session
- Legacy createTransaction kept for backward compat; sessionId is optional

Files changed:
- convex/schema.ts — new feeCollectionSessions table, billingPeriod on studentFees, sessionId+by_session on feeTransactions, collect_fees audit action
- convex/feeCollectionSessions.ts — collectFees mutation, getFutureMonths query, createFutureMonthFees mutation, getByStudent query
